flowRoot.flowPara: Person on the starting team throws the jack.
Valid throw must be in scoring area.
Get your boules closer to the jack then your opponent.
After the first boule is trown the team who's ball is not closest to the jack throws the next boule.
Each round is added to the last and the match is finished once one team scores 13 points
The winning team count the amount of boules they have closer to the jack
Once the team without the scoring advantage has run out of boules the other team resumes. Until none are left.
Team 1 has played 2 boules, but they are not closer so they play again.
